                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This letter is worn and faded like it was written years ago... And it's written to my mother...",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6d013a17-d3bd-4ed7-afee-af58e3c629ff",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>Dear Nora, You have my deepest sympathy for the loss of Donal. He was the best of brothers and the best of friends to me. There's not a moment goes by that I'm not thinking of him. </i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fb3e71b0-8fcb-4b55-b994-00d20fa869bd",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i> If you need any help with anything, feel free to ask me. I'll always be here for you and Donal's boy. Your loving Brother-in-Law, Shamus O'Conner</i>",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "8a0c9ea4-fe82-43bc-a28e-019e5924a03f",
                    "name": "Letter from Shamus",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "<i>Dear Nora,\n\nYou have my deepest sympathy for the loss of Donal. He was the best of brothers and the best of friends to me. There's not a moment goes by that I'm not thinking of him.\n\nIf you need any help with anything, feel free to ask me. I'll always be here for you and Donal's boy.\n\nYour loving Brother-in-Law,\nShamus O'Conner</i>\n\nSo if this Uncle Shamus was going to help us after my father died, why were Mama and I always living hand to mouth? Is there some reason my mother never mentioned him? I just don't know."
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2ff09c8e-8f50-43e2-8afa-ec3350ecb922",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I didn't know I had an Uncle Shamus! My mother never talked about him. I don't even really remember my father.",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4ddbe5ce-5199-4d81-8c4b-3802a1211621",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "So another mysterious letter that leaves me with more questions than answers... As if I didn't have enough questions already.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                }
            ]
        }
